messages.messageBody:
There's a good possibility we will be coming for a visit (5 - 7 days maybe a
couple more) to Wilmington the last week of November and wanted to know about
the possibility of meeting up with some RU-ers from that area. DH is working
down there and we'll be staying with him in his hotel and have free days and
the weekend to explore and have fun! The boys (8 & 3) and I have never been
to North Carolina and would love to meet up with someone or have someone show
us the sights or just some suggestions of what's good to do. Folks are
welcome to e-mail me offlist: Sanguinegirl83 @ aol.com

Thanks!
De
